title: Jokes Seth Can't Tell | Awkwafina
description:
Hear some jokes Seth can't tell, where Amber Ruffin and Jenny Hagel deliver punchlines that wouldn't sound right coming from Seth.

Then, Seth talks to Crazy Rich Asians star Awkwafina, who also takes a few more questions backstage at Studio 8G exclusively for the podcast.
